description.en: Switcheo builds decentralized platforms that break new ground, bringing you finance without limits. Whether you’re a battle-weary trader or are just making your first purchase, there’s nothing cryptic about crypto on Switcheo. Leading the pack with multiple world firsts, your time spent with Switcheo will be a worthwhile investment.

ico_data.short_desc: Switcheo is a Decentralized Exchange (DEX) built on the NEO platform. It allows for the trustless exchange of NEP-5 tokens and may expand to other cross-chain tokens in the future.

status_updates.description:
Gearing up for a new era of interoperability with Cosmos Stargate.

What exactly does this mean for Switcheo TradeHub? Read on 👇

blog.switcheo.network/cosmos

⚛️ 1000 $SWTH Giveaway! ⚛️
Like, RT & tag a Cosmos project you want to see interoperate with TradeHub for a chance to win!

Out with the old, in with the new. 

Read our April 2021 Updates blogpost here:
https://blog.switcheo.network/april-2021-updates/

Switcheo Exchange will officially be decommissioned on 30 April 2021 in favor of our layer 2 trading protocol, Switcheo TradeHub 🌅

Level up with Demex to enjoy lower fees and instant trades on SWTH, ETH, CEL markets and more. 

Read more here. 
https://bit.ly/31XPIXM

New quarterly futures markets for BTC and ETH are now up on Demex for mainnet beta trading!

Designated market makers are currently still performing final tests and will be launching on these new markets soon. 👀

👉 app.dem.exchange

💧 Great news for liquidity providers on Demex! Liquidity rewards will be continuing on for another 6 months! The update to extend the rewards will be going live today, 11 March 2021 at 3pm SGT. 

🕺🏽 More details in our newest blog post!
https://bit.ly/38vcsBT

👀 If you've been in the DeFi space long enough, you're likely to have heard the term "Layer 2".

Demex is a Layer 2 DEX. But what does that really mean? We dive into the details in our newest blog post.

https://bit.ly/2ZsuAr5

We're excited to introduce the highly-anticipated ZilSwap governance token, $ZWAP!

The new ZRC-2 governance token marks a significant milestone in ZilSwap's journey towards true #decentralization.

Check out our blog post to find out more details about $ZWAP, and how the token will be distributed in the coming weeks! 🔥
https://bit.ly/3sKVo3u
